{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_10_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 こんな土砂降りってある！？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ当日か\n遙子さんにとっていい経験になるよう、頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s finally the day.\nI have to do my best to make this a good experience for Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.6666667,
          "startTime": 6.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.3333333,
          "startTime": 7.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう！　お迎えありがとう\n今日はいい天気になって良かったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning! Thanks for picking me up.\nI’m glad the weather’s so nice today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.8047389666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もっとお洒落したかったなぁ\n{user}君もスーツ姿だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish I had dressed up more‚ though.\nSince you’re wearing a suit‚ {user}-kun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "万が一、芸能関係の記者に見つかっても\nこの格好なら仕事って言えますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we happen to get spotted by entertainment reporters‚\nI can just say we’re working since I’m in this outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6994778632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "それもお忍びデートみたいで悪くないわね\nあ、いけない、鍵忘れちゃった。ちょっと待ってて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me feel like a secret date‚ which isn’t bad either.\nOh‚ no‚ I forgot my key. Wait a sec――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8867.188803500003,
          "startTime": 35.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.3229707399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、嘘っ！？　雨！？\n急に？　しかもこんな土砂降りってある！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ no way!? Rain!?\nAll of a sudden? And what's with this crazy downpour!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、寮に入って！\nずぶ濡れになっちゃう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ get inside the dorm!\nYou’ll get soaked!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 51.0337184745
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.2837184745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな……\nこんな大雨じゃ出かけられそうにないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad…\nIt doesn’t look like we can go out in this heavy rain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "なんで雨なのよ～！\n天気予報は晴れだったのに～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why is it raining~?!\nThe forecast said it would be sunny~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ……とはいえ今日を逃すと\nもう撮影までオフの日がないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well well… if we miss today‚\nwe won’t have another day off before the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "……いいわ、それなら今日はおうちでじっくり二人で\n楽しみましょ。ちょうど夜まで、誰もいないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fine‚ then let’s just stay home and have fun together today.\nNo one's coming back until tonight‚ anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8545452275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "変な言い方はやめて下さい。でも外は大雨ですし\nおうちデート、というやつにしますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t say it like that. But it’s pouring outside‚\nso shall we have a… “home date”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "おうちデート！　ふふ、{user}君から\n提案してもらえるなんて嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A home date! Fufu‚ I’m so happy\nyou suggested it‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "私、何か遊べるものを持ってくるわね\nおうちデート、おうちデート～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go get something to play with.\nHome date‚ home date~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4666681926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5604.0823461,
          "startTime": 100.1000015259
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "随分はしゃいでるなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s really excited about this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7064407188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two Hours Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0510212261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君\nこの形のピースを探してくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚\ncan you find a piece that fits this shape?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nあ、このピースじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nAh‚ isn’t it this piece?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、それよそれ！\nナイスピース、サニーピース！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes yes‚ that’s it!\nNice piece‚ Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか、その謎の掛け声は\n遙子さん、オフはいつもこんな感じなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with that weird cheer?\nHaruko-san‚ is this how you always are when you’re off work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "だって、一人で黙ってパズルをやっても盛り上がりに\n欠けるじゃない？　これでトドメよ、サニーピース！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because if I do a puzzle alone in silence‚ it’ll be a bit\nanticlimactic‚ right? This is the finishing touch‚ Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（パズルって完成まで特に盛り上がらずに）\n（静かに楽しむ趣味だと思ってた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I thought puzzles were a hobby you enjoyed quietly）\n（without getting excited until they’re finished…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ～、完成完成！\nねぇ、そろそろお腹空かない？　お昼にしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew~‚ complete complete!\nHey‚ are you getting hungry? Let’s have lunch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。準備、俺も手伝いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. I’ll help you get ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5045824209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "パスタ、凄く美味しかったです。スープに前菜まで\n付くと、お店のコース料理みたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The pasta was delicious. With the soup and appetizer‚\nit’s like a course meal at a restaurant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.1666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にお料理するのが楽しくて、つい張り切っちゃった\n……そういえば、あの時も一緒にパスタを食べたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got a little carried away because it was fun cooking together.\n…Come to think of it‚ we had pasta together back then too‚ didn’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、高校のテスト前の時ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you mean when we studied for the high school exams?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7703734557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
